{"id": 1216, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在生活中有哪些心理负担特别大的时候？ ", "description": "说真的，我也不知道自己在患得患失什么。（题图来自：Faye Moorhouse）", "record_count": 4702, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160912231046d0xEIPoDjYB9A8Tr.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-15T17:00:06Z", "options": [{"id": 116480, "content": "突然没事做的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759823}, {"id": 116481, "content": "考试成绩发之前一分钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453039}, {"id": 116738, "content": "分手后对方过得很轻松", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649010}, {"id": 116483, "content": "工作日却无事可做的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634400}, {"id": 116739, "content": "女朋友生气，但你不知道怎么回事的时候～", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760416}, {"id": 137476, "content": "上班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689742}, {"id": 116484, "content": "理智中必须做的事 却没有行动进展", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726099}, {"id": 116740, "content": "别人问为什么无男朋友的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725661}, {"id": 116996, "content": "想到我这样的性格缺陷会影响生活质量的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760896}, {"id": 117252, "content": "事情很多或者是没事做的时候，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734982}, {"id": 116485, "content": "计划了要做的事，却没有做的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725205}, {"id": 116741, "content": "将家人介绍给别人认识的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725661}, {"id": 137734, "content": "发现进展缓慢的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841299}, {"id": 116486, "content": "  看到女朋友分享她生活的一点一滴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759830}, {"id": 116742, "content": "工作汇报，自己的做的很屎，别人却做的很好的时候…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605591}, {"id": 116487, "content": "没有加班的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739913}, {"id": 116743, "content": "梦想和现实差别太大的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694172}, {"id": 116744, "content": "我喜欢你你知道吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759855}, {"id": 117512, "content": "有了目标去施行的过程中开始怀疑自己的能力和现实的残酷的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763498}, {"id": 116489, "content": "马上睡着被吵醒的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449790}, {"id": 116490, "content": "iPhone7plus第一天就预定了还没发货的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154291}, {"id": 116746, "content": "工作的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760424}, {"id": 117002, "content": "工作中需要完成的，无力推动的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 757440}, {"id": 116747, "content": "家里人内斗经常黑着脸的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741741}, {"id": 117515, "content": "老是犹豫不决的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667777}, {"id": 116748, "content": "家里催婚的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676020}, {"id": 117260, "content": "特别想被爸妈认可却不得不管他们借钱，然后还赔了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752467}, {"id": 119564, "content": "舍友总是开玩笑 受不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773552}, {"id": 116493, "content": "和一个打呼噜严重，而又不承认的人住一个寝室，就是遭罪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722844}, {"id": 116749, "content": "不想事情  冲动做事  做了又超级后悔  想东想西   心理负担真的蛮大的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535088}, {"id": 117261, "content": "看到别人因为我出事的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 731253}, {"id": 116750, "content": "最近常梦到马上要考研了，却还没来得及复习数学。梦里一堆泰勒展开公式，勒得我好窒息！明明考研已经过去快十年了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760429}, {"id": 119054, "content": "和陌生人对话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770854}, {"id": 116495, "content": "无能为力的时候吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759850}, {"id": 116751, "content": "别人都聊的很high，而我不想说话的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760432}, {"id": 117007, "content": "感觉自己好像很忙，但是又好像什么事也没做", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760907}, {"id": 116496, "content": "想家的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747459}, {"id": 152337, "content": "无能为力的时候\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898955}, {"id": 116497, "content": "缺乏自我生活的安全感", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 756174}, {"id": 117265, "content": "突然有计划外的开支！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209229}, {"id": 116498, "content": "想想现在的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759409}, {"id": 116754, "content": "每次，中介来电问“一套40平的一居室400万，要不要？”的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759755}, {"id": 117010, "content": "离成功越来越远，而自己还提不上劲的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713837}, {"id": 117266, "content": "突然有计划外的开支！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209229}, {"id": 116499, "content": "努力升职却不加薪，节假日回不了家想父母的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749950}, {"id": 116755, "content": "忙忙碌碌却没有收获", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760434}, {"id": 117011, "content": "拖延症，啊呀呀呀！~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721518}, {"id": 117267, "content": "事业无成 前途迷茫的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761847}, {"id": 120339, "content": "晚睡早起做的事，结果却是无用功", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 768994}, {"id": 116500, "content": "看到别人都很努力的时候，有目标时候，自己缺无所事事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752779}]}